comments[8]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-02-19T00:16:29.256Z",maintainer-agent,"Planned changeset: harden deterministic serialization utilities for JSON-like and edge-case inputs, add explicit unit coverage for sorting/undefined-skipping/fallback coercion behavior, and include the core serializer utility in enforced coverage scope."
  "2026-02-19T00:17:34.181Z",maintainer-agent,"Implemented serializer hardening: stableStringify now canonicalizes Date values and respects object toJSON outputs when they differ from the original object, while preserving deterministic sorted-key behavior for plain objects and undefined-field omission."
  "2026-02-19T00:39:25.049Z",maintainer-agent,"Follow-up changeset: replaced generic fallback stringification in stableStringify with explicit bigint/undefined/symbol/function handling plus deterministic terminal fallback token to satisfy lint quality constraints without changing canonical object ordering."
  "2026-02-19T00:41:12.844Z",maintainer-agent,"Coverage follow-up fix: refactored serializer type-branch flow to eliminate an unreachable terminal fallback line while retaining deterministic handling for bigint/undefined/symbol/function/Date/toJSON/object values."
  "2026-02-19T00:41:45.626Z",maintainer-agent,"Type-safety correction: switched serializer branch guards back to direct typeof checks so TypeScript can narrow unknown values correctly without reintroducing non-deterministic fallback behavior."
  "2026-02-19T00:42:51.606Z",maintainer-agent,Added serializer unit assertion for anonymous function fallback to close remaining branch-coverage gap in core/shared/serialization.ts.
  "2026-02-19T01:06:56.887Z",maintainer-agent,"Lint follow-up: replaced typeof-undefined check with direct undefined comparison and moved namedFallback helper to test-module scope to satisfy static quality warnings without behavior changes."
  "2026-02-19T01:28:01.655Z",maintainer-agent,"Evidence: node dist/cli.js test pm-vdh --run --timeout 1800 --json passed all linked checks (coverage + targeted determinism tests + build). Coverage gate remains 100% lines/branches/functions/statements, including src/core/shared/serialization.ts. Regression sweeps passed with no failures: node dist/cli.js test-all --status in_progress --timeout 1800 --json => items=5 linked_tests=23 passed=22 failed=0 skipped=1; node dist/cli.js test-all --status closed --timeout 1800 --json => items=13 linked_tests=34 passed=31 failed=0 skipped=3."
